snippet: Code-hopping centre Sonny Bill Williams has been fast-tracked into the big time for the All Blacks as coach Steve Hansen named virtually a full-strength team on Thursday to face England at Twickenham on Saturday....

headline.print_headline: Sonny Bill to Face England, No Carter in New Zealand Squad
headline.main: Sonny Bill to Face England, No Carter in New Zealand Squad

lead_paragraph: Code-hopping centre Sonny Bill Williams has been fast-tracked into the big time for the All Blacks as coach Steve Hansen named virtually a full-strength team on Thursday to face England at Twickenham on Saturday.
